odulates the frequency, rate, or extent of an acute inflammatory response.\" [GOC:add]\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21853:intersection_of: regulates GO:0002526 ! acute inflammatory response\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21857:name: negative regulation of acute inflammatory response\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21859:def: \"Any process that stops, prevents, or reduces the frequency, rate, or extent of an acute inflammatory response.\" [GOC:add]\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21860:synonym: \"down regulation of acute inflammatory response\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21861:synonym: \"down-regulation of acute inflammatory response\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21862:synonym: \"downregulation of acute inflammatory response\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21863:synonym: \"inhibition of acute inflammatory response\" NARROW []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21865:intersection_of: negatively_regulates GO:0002526 ! acute inflammatory response\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21869:name: positive regulation of acute inflammatory response\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21871:def: \"Any process that activates or increases the frequency, rate, or extent of an acute inflammatory response.\" [GOC:add]\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21872:synonym: \"activation of acute inflammatory response\" NARROW []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21873:synonym: \"stimulation of acute inflammatory response\" NARROW []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21874:synonym: \"up regulation of acute inflammatory response\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21875:synonym: \"up-regulation of acute inflammatory response\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21876:synonym: \"upregulation of acute inflammatory response\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21878:intersection_of: positively_regulates GO:0002526 ! acute inflammatory response\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21882:name: regulation of chronic inflammatory response\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:21884:def: \"Any process that modulates the frequency, rate, or extent of a chronic inflammatory