en organism.\" [GOC:fj, GOC:jl, PMID:10620318, PMID:21150580]\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264873:synonym: \"envenomation resulting in muscle damage in another organism\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264874:synonym: \"envenomation resulting in muscle damage in other organism\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264875:is_a: GO:0140138 ! venom-mediated disruption of anatomical structure in another organism\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264881:name: venom-mediated myocyte killing in another organism\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264883:def: \"A process that begins with venom being forced into an organism by the bite or sting of another organism, killing heart myocytes and ultimately resulting in muscle damage in the bitten organism.\" [GOC:fj, GOC:jl, PMID:10620318, PMID:21150580]\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264884:synonym: \"envenomation resulting in myocyte killing causing muscle damage in other organism\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264885:synonym: \"envenomation resulting in myocyte killing in another organism\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264886:synonym: \"envenomation resulting in myocyte killing in other organism\" EXACT []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264888:is_a: GO:0044521 ! venom-mediated muscle damage in another organism\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264894:name: venom-mediated disruption of extracellular matrix in another organism\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264896:def: \"A process that begins with venom being forced into an organism by the bite or sting of another organism, damaging the extracellular matrix of a cell.\" [GOC:fj, GOC:jl, PMID:20398688, PMID:21150580, PMID:33460638, PMID:37006255, PMID:41241197]\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264897:synonym: \"envenomation resulting in damage of muscle extracellular matrix causing muscle necrosis in other organism\" NARROW []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264898:synonym: \"envenomation resulting in damage of muscle extracellular matrix in another organism\" NARROW []\nsrc/ontology/go-edit.obo:264899:synonym: \"enveno